data.description:
Motivated Seller! Welcome to luxury living of Goodyear, nestled within the prestigious guard-gated community of PebbleCreek! As you enter, you're greeted with soaring ceilings in the grand foyer. The Cambria plan revolves around a spacious great room with vaulted ceilings, bar area, chef's kitchen with granite counters, loads of cabinet space, large breakfast area flowing seamlessly to the outdoors. The primary suite is accompanied by a relaxing sitting room, en-suite bath with separate tub, walk-in shower, make-up vanity finished with a dual sink vanity. 
Step out back to a covered patio and a professionally landscaped low maintenance backyard. PebbleCreek  community offers golfing, restaurants, social clubs, fitness center, indoor/outdoor pools, tennis, walking trails and so much more.
